properties.areaDesc: Waters from Pigeon Point to Point Pinos 10-60 NM
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued February 15 at 2:38AM PST until February 16 at 3:00PM PST by NWS San Francisco CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Seas 8 to 10 feet at 15 seconds expected.

* WHERE...Waters from Pigeon Point to Point Pinos 10-60 NM.

* WHEN...For the Small Craft Advisory, until 3 PM PST this
afternoon. For the Small Craft Advisory, from 9 AM to 3 PM PST
Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 3 PM PST THIS AFTERNOON... ...SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 9 AM TO 3 PM PST SUNDAY
